---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="whois"
    description="Who runs this place?"
>
    <div class="whois-shell">

        <section class="panel">
            <div class="terminal-counter">
                <div class="terminal-titlebar">
                    <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                    <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                    <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                    <span class="terminal-title">terminal — whois adam</span>
                </div>
                <div class="terminal-screen">

                    <figure class="crt-frame" aria-label="Portrait of Adam">
                        <div class="ascii-top" aria-hidden="true">
                            <span>╔</span><span class="ascii-hfill"></span><span>╗</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ascii-mid">
                            <span class="ascii-vfill" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <div class="crt-photo-wrap">
                                <img src="/adam_headshot.png" class="crt-photo" alt="Adam" />
                            </div>
                            <span class="ascii-vfill" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ascii-bot" aria-hidden="true">
                            <span>╚</span><span class="ascii-hfill"></span><span>╝</span>
                        </div>
                    </figure>

                    <p class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">coffee$</span> whois adam</p>
                    <p class="terminal-line dim">querying registry...</p>
                    <p></p><p></p>
                    <p class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt"></span> Handle: <span class="tval cyan">Adam</span></p>
                    <p class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt"></span> Role: <span class="tval green">gamer / cat dad / software engineer</span></p>
                    <p class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt"></span> Status: <span class="tval yellow">online, probably debugging something</span></p>
                    <p class="terminal-line dim">---</p>
                    <p class="terminal-line dim">Record last updated: just today and never again.</p>
                    <p class="terminal-line dim">---</p>

                    <p class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt"></span> <span class="tval cyan">// about</span></p>
                    <p class="terminal-output">I'm Adam. I make coffee, play games, write software, cook food, and share space with my partner and two incredible cats who can jump through hoops but still can't understand that I don't want them on my keyboard.</p>
                    <p class="terminal-output">This site is <em>not</em> a portfolio. It's not optimized for LinkedIn. It has no cookie consent modal, no newsletter popup, no "We value your privacy" banner that values nothing. It's just a website.</p>
                    <p class="terminal-output">The web peaked somewhere around 2005&ndash;2009. We had weird personal sites, RSS feeds, web rings and forums where people were creativity was rampant and we found each other through community, not algorithms. Then everything turned into a walled garden with ads, a subscription tier, an app (sorry my fault), a "platform", and it just wasn't as fun as it used to be.</p>
                    <p class="terminal-output">Here I am, back where I started with HTML, CSS and some markdown. RIP flash.</p>

                    <p class="terminal-line dim">---</p>

                    <p class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt"></span> <span class="tval cyan">// elsewhere</span></p>
                    <p class="terminal-output">I'm on the internet in a few places. Reluctantly.</p>
                    <p class="terminal-line terminal-link-line"><span class="prompt"></span> <a href="https://github.com/AdamWardVGP" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a> &mdash; where my actual code lives</p>

                    <p class="terminal-line dim">---</p>

                    <p class="terminal-line terminal-prompt-line">
                        <span class="prompt">adam@coffee:~$</span>
                        <span class="blink-cursor" aria-hidden="true">&#x2588;</span>
                    </p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.whois-shell {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
}

/* ══ ASCII-framed CRT portrait ══ */

.crt-frame {
    display: block;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    float: right;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 1rem;
    width: 160px;
    max-width: 160px;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(127, 219, 202, 0.55);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
    background: none;
}

.ascii-top,
.ascii-bot {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
}

.ascii-hfill {
    flex: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 1em;
}

.ascii-hfill::before {
    content: "════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════";
    display: block;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
}

.ascii-mid {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
}

.ascii-vfill {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 195px;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(127, 219, 202, 0.55);
    white-space: pre;
}

.ascii-vfill::before {
    content: "║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║\A║";
    display: block;
}

.crt-photo-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #000;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    position: relative;
}

.crt-photo {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 195px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    filter: grayscale(1) sepia(1) hue-rotate(85deg) contrast(1.2) brightness(0.7);
    animation: crt-flicker 10s infinite;
}

.crt-photo-wrap::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        transparent 0,
        transparent 2px,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 2px,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 4px
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
}

.crt-photo-wrap::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 35%, rgba(100, 219, 127, 0.12) 0%, transparent 65%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(100, 219, 127, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 3;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
}

@keyframes crt-flicker {
    0%, 86%, 88.5%, 100% {
        filter: grayscale(1) sepia(1) hue-rotate(85deg) contrast(1.2) brightness(0.7);
    }
    87% {
        filter: grayscale(1) sepia(1) hue-rotate(85deg) contrast(1.6) brightness(0.45);
    }
    88% {
        filter: grayscale(1) sepia(1) hue-rotate(85deg) contrast(1.25) brightness(0.65) blur(1px);
    }
}

/* ══ terminal text ══ */

.tval { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; }
.tval.cyan   { color: var(--accent-cyan); }
.tval.green  { color: var(--accent-green); }
.tval.yellow { color: var(--accent-yellow); }

.terminal-output {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
}

.terminal-output + .terminal-output {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.terminal-output em {
    color: var(--accent-yellow);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.terminal-link-line {
    margin-top: 0.4rem !important;
}

.terminal-link-line a {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
}

.terminal-link-line a:hover {
    color: var(--text-bright);
}

/* ══ blinking cursor ══ */

.terminal-prompt-line {
    clear: both;
    margin-top: 0.85rem !important;
}


/* ══ stack ══ */

.stack-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.stack-col h3 { margin-top: 0; }

.stack-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
}

.stack-list li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.38rem 0.6rem;
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
}

.stack-list.nope li { color: var(--text-secondary); }
.stack-list.nope code { color: var(--accent-red); }

/* ══ timeline ══ */

.timeline {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
}

.tl-entry {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.55rem 0;
}

.tl-entry::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.38rem;
    top: 1rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-cyan);
    border: 2px solid var(--bg-primary);
}

.tl-year {
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent-yellow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding-top: 0.18rem;
    text-align: right;
}

.tl-body strong { color: var(--text-bright); font-size: 0.95rem; }

.tl-body p {
    margin: 0.2rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

/* ══ responsive ══ */

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .crt-frame {
        float: none;
        margin: 0 0 0.85rem 0;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .crt-photo {
        height: 220px;
        object-position: center top;
    }

    .ascii-vfill {
        height: 220px;
    }

    .stack-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>